src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過整得幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53492c8d30b7abb0f03b966205d01717624d22dd","tid":114973,"uid":38407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea272387972a46d898ffb6de6bd8c36319549178","tid":114973,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"呢隊野d關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129c0dbb46ac180640c1db4e907d369d8d3fa70f","tid":114973,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"Areum唔係話過花英最照顧佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋個陣有kbs pd 出黎講說話，話花英俾人丟拐杖出門口，sistar Dasom 仲黎安慰佢架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6303d6302b7977b8629e879a01c97ad54550a9f","tid":114973,"uid":34111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Areum唔係話過花英最照顧佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋個陣有kbs pd 出黎講說話，話花英俾人丟拐杖出門口，sistar Dasom 仲黎安慰佢架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家先爆，顯然想做低花英啦"},{"pid":"2f2e36ce76fafef1da82950d5648a21eb8b58aef","tid":114973,"uid":70343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Areum唔係話過花英最照顧佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋個陣有kbs pd 出黎講說話，話花英俾人丟拐杖出門口，sistar Dasom 仲黎安慰佢架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n恐嚇嗰個係孝英<br />\n唔知關唔關花英事<br />\n<br />\n或者大家都真係演技出眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ab0fd9322989a2dbcc6b18409cfb3372b6